          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王老爷邀酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皂隶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请回。\n王老爷邀酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "门子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王老爷邀酒三次。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打道！"
        },
        {
          "character": "门子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打道！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖大开门〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "皂隶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "按院老爷到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王国辅上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "按院老爷到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷出迎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，宪公祖！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖曲牌收〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宪公祖，按临敝地，治生尚未请教，多多有罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生望隆山斗，晚生特来领教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢，请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜宪公祖，豸冠铁柱，功名不减于延年；白简绣衣，謇萼无分于刁曜。圣天\n子眷注方新，治生辈共沾雨露。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生亲总六师，请白无惭于张奋；得专九伐，袞冕荷忝于陈骞。朝野俱瞻，\n华夷仰望。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒完。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是！\n上酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王国辅 （同玉芙蓉） 霜威凛似秋，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "剑气冲牛斗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羡丰神，金茎玉露难俦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "洛日补天事业优。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皂隶 （夹白） 谢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "院子 （夹白） 谢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王国辅 （同玉芙蓉） 为观风遍诹，愿恭承善诱，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庶得免愆尤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宪公祖，小园虽则荒芜，花草颇觉烂漫，还请宪公祖一游，以增泉石之光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久慕名园，实切企仰，只是惭无好句以赠，恐花神笑其不韵耳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。\n吩咐开了园门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宪公祖请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "深感主人多缱绻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还从曲径玩芳菲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖、王国辅",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐继祖、王国辅、皂隶、院子同下。〖春日景和〗。苏夫人上。〖曲牌收〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啾啾唧唧，割肚牵肠，怎生了得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王小姐上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "终日里重门静掩，还怕向堂前悲泣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，我自托身府中，又是十八年矣。虽则蒙小姐另眼相待，情同骨肉，不知\n我婆婆在家安否，叔叔奉养如何？几次要寄书回去，又无便人，故此终日放心\n不下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我见母亲闷闷不乐，已吩咐园丁开了园门，且到亭上散步一回如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，小姐请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏夫人 （月儿高） 花阴鹤唳，闲庭缀蓓蕾，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王小姐 （月儿高） 看香霭飞芳径，空翠涵春水。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏夫人 （月儿高） 我怕向深林，闷把栏杆倚，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我生枉羁人世，死也为怨鬼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王小姐 （夹白） 母亲亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（月儿高） 且请开怀莫皱眉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏夫人 （夹白） 小姐吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（月儿高） 我念到家园意似痴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何这等慌张？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷，按院老爷游玩，请小姐、苏夫人快些回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐、苏夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到太湖石畔那里躲一躲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欲遣闷怀芳径步，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不期花里有人来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏夫人、王小姐同下。徐继祖、王国辅同上。〖春日景和〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宪公祖请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖曲牌收〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓！昔人云：极目无由赏，闲游不避喧。今日对此名园，不觉形神俱化。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖春日景和〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忒过誉了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面什么所在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "名曰江天阁，可以望江，请宪公祖一登。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欲穷千里目，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更上一层楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看茶！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐继祖、王国辅同下。〖曲牌收〗。苏夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲见了那位官长，为何啼哭起来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，方才那位官长呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 听声气，看他容貌奇，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依稀与我夫主一样的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今有十八纪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不到官府去吿理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我一向要到官府去吿理，只因我是女流，不好出乖露丑。今日见此御史若不吿\n理，终无雪寃之日了㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日爹爹请他饮酒，怎好去唐突他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐说你哪里话来？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 他受朝廷爵位，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "况且行道替天，料能除奸宄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何惜微躯碎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 小姐吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 何须畏，拼履危，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日一鸣冤，胜似鬼为励。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是不可去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放手，呀啐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏夫人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王小姐下。〖春日景和〗。徐继祖、王国辅同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宪公祖请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生请！妙吓，又是一洞天了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太过奖了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这又是什么所在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是叙香亭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是清辉阁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一发幽雅。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖曲牌收〗。苏夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀爷爷，冤枉吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才狗才，好不小心！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王国辅下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带来亭子上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "皂隶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！\n妇人当面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷，冤枉吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这妇人，有何冤枉，从实说上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷听禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 我是儒门裔宦室妻，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫君当日遭祸奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你丈夫叫甚名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我丈夫姓苏名云，进士出身，前任兰溪县知县。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是位夫人，请起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏公遭甚奇祸？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 只为赴任到兰溪，江心遇强队，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把我丈夫呵登时立毙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亏煞他贤弟——"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个什么贤弟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "其时正在危急之际，亏他兄弟徐熊，哄醉强徒，将奴放出后门，才得脱离虎口\n㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事有几年了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀爷爷吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 有十八载沉冤，怨气弥天地。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若得获凶徒，我命甘捐弃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人请回，待本院回衙，与你细查便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幸亏清廉吏，得雪覆盆冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏夫人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请王老爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "门子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王老爷有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王国辅上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓宪公祖，治生多多有罪了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！老先生，那苏夫人为何在此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖，有个缘故。治生当日，生一小女，要唤个乳娘，有人领她进来的。后来晓\n得她是好人家儿女，落难到此，就不叫她乳娘，合宅都称她苏夫人，所以在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。下官未到任时，就闻知此事，知识那苏老先生遭此惨祸，实为可怜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "便是。今日薄设水酒，聊以表情，不道有此一番唐突，治生多多有罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老先生说哪里话？下官蒙圣恩重委，原为伸冤理枉，这样事正该与她昭雪，老\n先生何言有罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "足见宪公祖凤裁，可敬吓可羡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小桌已完。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "简慢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐侍候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "门子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各役侍候！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖大开门〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐继祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐继祖下。〖曲牌收〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷辛苦了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才狗才，哪个放苏夫人出来叫喊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是园丁之故，与我们无干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此把园丁跪着，将我名帖，到徐按台那里请罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王国辅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放肆的狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王国辅下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是哪里说起？与园丁算账！"
        }
      ],
